The '''Anapolla Musical Splash''' was a musical attraction at [[Lamuir IV]]'s [[Priole Danna Festival]] showcasing several different genres of music from [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy's]] most famous recording artists, as well as new performers.<ref name="HNN45">{{HoloNetNewsWeb|45|life/13228_1.html|Priole Danna Festival Still a Go}}</ref> A 5-[[Standard day/Legends|day]] event, the Splash included pieces from many [[Human/Legends|Human]] and [[Alien/Legends|alien]] traditions. Many artist who played the Splash tended to emerge as powerful and popular stars, and many attending the event were usually recording studio representatives.<ref name="GNN3" />

